00:35:22.300 --> 00:35:23.300
[laughter]

00:35:23.300 --> 00:35:24.300
&gt;&gt;STEVE GROVE: How kind.

00:35:24.300 --> 00:35:25.300
&gt;&gt;ANDERSON COOPER: Yes.

00:35:25.300 --> 00:35:26.300
&gt;&gt;STEVE GROVE: Very thoughtful.

