the people are wanting. So, what can we do

00:37:26.690 --> 00:37:32.309
with social technologies that Americans aren't
using and what can the media do to help us?

00:37:32.309 --> 00:37:35.599
&gt;&gt;ANDERSON COOPER: Wow. That's interesting.
