changing?

00:40:55.410 --> 00:40:56.410
&gt;&gt;ANDERSON COOPER: Right.

00:40:56.410 --> 00:40:57.410
&gt;&gt;MALE AUDIENCE MEMBER #3: What you see as
their future--.

00:40:57.410 --> 00:40:58.799
&gt;&gt;ANDERSON COOPER: Well, I hope you put a
stop to this.

00:40:58.799 --> 00:40:59.799
[laughter]

00:40:59.799 --> 00:41:00.799
